    // About-us
    section.about_us.section-padding(style='padding-top: 1%')
        .container
            ul.coustom-breadcrumb
                li
                    a(href='/', style='color: #1e96fe') Home
                li
                    a(style='color: #1e96fe') >
                li(style='color: #1e96fe') About Us
            .section-header.text-center
                h2(style='color: #2e6da4') Blue World Auto
                p(style='text-align: justify')
                    | Blue World Auto is the product of more than 20 years of combined experience between the two
                    | companys, Balla Group and Muhanad Cars. It is essential for a company to be founded on certain
                    | values, that’s why the founders of Blue World Auto began aligning values like integrity,
                    | honesty, and professionalism with the company's branding strategy, creating a seamless and
                    | headache-free experience for our customers. We believe that a flexible and skilled team coupled
                    | with clear and integrated values creates a strong foundational core for Blue World Auto.
                p(style='text-align: justify')
                    | Blue World Auto is willing to distribute vehicles in Kurdistan and Iraq, due to our experience
                    | and professional staff, we will be your most effective partner in Delivering your products and
                    | services to the customers in Iraq.
    section.why_choose_us.section-padding.gray-bg
        .container
            .section-header.text-center.gray-bg
                h2 Balla Group
                h2.text-left(style='font-size:150%') History :
                p(style='text-align: justify')
                    | Was established by several of professional business experts and highly qualified engineers.
                    | Balla has grown over the years, into a major conglomerate with entities in different industry
                    | sectors. All of these companies work together for the rebuilding, restructuring and betterment
                    | of Iraq based in Sulaimaniyah.
                p(style='text-align: justify')
                    | BALLA is an all-round contracting company providing solution for a variety projects and are
                    | capable of delivering international standard services and products to all level of consumers,
                    | home, business and government Sector. Balla handles projects of all sizes, either on its own
                    | or by forming project groups with selecting associates.
                br
                h2.text-left(style='font-size:150%') Visions :
                p(style='text-align: justify')
                    | Our vision is to reach maximum in offer the high quality Service and Solution to consumers.
                    | Reconstruct Iraq country in a very high speed in to a modernize country Mission.
                br
                h2.text-left(style='font-size:150%') Mission :
                p(style='text-align: justify')
                    | is to provide a high quality, cost effective and to modernize customer’s life by offer the new
                    | design, modern construction, and development services and Import high quality material.
    section.why_choose_us.section-padding
        .container
            .section-header.text-center
                h2 Muhannad Cars
                h2.text-left(style='font-size:150%') History :
                p(style='text-align: justify')
                    | Muhanad Cars Company was established in 1999 and is the first company (in trading cars) to
                    | import cars in Iraqi Kurdistan in Erbil governorate. Now operating in the market with great
                    | skills and efficiency, controlling the import of saloon (passenger)cars, SUVs, armored vehicles,
                    | buses, freezers and ambulance. Moreover, our company relies on selffinancing sources
                    | and provides after sales services whether it is deals or retail Having more than twenty years
                    | of rich experience in automotive and marketing, the brand name has become one of the best
                    | known names in the automotive market, not only in the local Iraqi market but also throughout
                    | the Middle East and the Arabian Gulf region.
                br
                h2.text-left(style='font-size:150%') Visions :
                p(style='text-align: justify')
                    | Muhanad Cars Group aims to meet the needs of the local Iraqi market in general and the Kurdistan
                    | region in particular.
                    | Provide a variety of vehicles and cars, where demand is concentrated mainly in the center, the
                    | southern and northern regions of Iraq.
                br
                h2.text-left(style='font-size:150%') Mission :
                p(style='text-align: justify') To remain at the forefront of the market.
                p(style='text-align: justify')  • Obtaining exclusive contracts with international trade agencies.
                p(style='text-align: justify')
                    | • Providing quality services, excellent and after sales services, an effective presence in the
                    | market, loyalty programs and paying more attention to customer satisfaction.
